Today is President Biden's birthday, Peter.

We're so grateful to have a president who leads our nation with integrity and empathy. President Biden campaigned on a promise to restore the soul of our nation, and he's been leading by example since his inauguration.

Just think of how far we've come since President Biden was sworn into office less than a year ago today. With the passage of the American Rescue Plan earlier this year, we've gotten thousands of folks back to work and administered millions of life-saving vaccines. We've also passed numerous pieces of historic legislation -- including the Infrastructure Investment and American Jobs Act.

**These are accomplishments worth celebrating, and what better day to do so than on President Biden 's birthday?[ Sign President Biden's birthday card to help us celebrate him and all that he's helped us accomplish as a nation. ](https://act.myngp.com/el/VuPneWUSOBK40ZV2XofZ6ciTQ3FBNCjbVoWNIH86w68=/GX7TKQyuI69wvyA1DnxIPsv-pnZ6AwnF8iMoai40Jcs=?ms=em21_211120_BB_engg_gq_act___TK_ettx&refcode=em21_211120_BB_engg_gq_act___TK_ettx&source=em21_211120_BB_engg_gq_act___TK_ettx&utm_campaign=em21_211120_BB_engg_gq_act___TK_ettx&utm_medium=email&em={{EmailAddress%2CDefaultTo%3D}}&fn={{FirstName%2CDefaultTo%3D}}&ln={{LastName%2CDefaultTo%3D}}&pc={{ZipCode%2CDefaultTo%3D}}&contactdata={{ContactData}}
