President Biden proposed a big, ambitious agenda when he ran for office. It's clear he's not giving up the fight -- and neither is Derek. Derek is proud to work in partnership with the Biden Administration to deliver even more results to the American people.

Derek and President Biden are both committed to building upon the successes of the American Rescue Plan, the Infrastructure Investment and Jobs Act, and more to keep moving our country forward. And our team is working every day to make sure Derek and President Biden have a strong grassroots team by their side to help get the job done for Americans and our nation's future.

